"number' should be '2', and 'Electrical Type' should be 'Power input'."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Getting_Started_in_KiCad.adoc:811
msgid ""
"Repeat the place-pin steps, this time 'Pin name' should be 'GND', 'Pin "
"number' should be '3', and 'Electrical Type' should be 'Power output'. "
