#. type: Plain text
#: Getting_Started_in_KiCad.adoc:817
msgid ""
"Next, draw the contour of the component. Click on the 'Add rectangle' icon "
"image:images/add_rectangle.png[add_rectangle_png]. We want to draw a "
"rectangle next to the pins, as shown below. To do this, click where you want "
"the top left corner of the rectangle to be. Click again where you want the "
"bottom right corner of the rectangle to be.  image:"
"images/10000000000000DD000000946E66C399."
"png[10000000000000DD000000946E66C399_png]"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Getting_Started_in_KiCad.adoc:821
