"any confirmation messages that appear.  The new schematic component is now "
"done and available in the library indicated in the window title bar."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: Getting_Started_in_KiCad.adoc:837
msgid ""
"You can now close the Component library editor window. You will return to "
